data.description: Inviting 4 Bedroom Home on almost an acre lot! Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the open and airy layout that connects the kitchen, living room and dining room creating effortless entertaining and easy flow between spaces. Patio doors off the dining room open to a 3 season room, making a seamless transition between indoor and outdoor living. The kitchen features ample counter space & a breakfast bar, providing a casual spot for quick meals or a gathering place for friends and family. The main floor also includes a spacious master suite with ensuite bathroom & walk-in closet. Upstairs, you'll find three additional bedrooms and a full bathroom with a double vanity to ensure convenience and comfort for all. Choose to enjoy your park-like setting from the front or back deck, or 3 season room - great for outdoor gatherings, barbecues, or simply unwinding and taking in the peaceful surroundings. The walk-out basement offers additional living space for recreation and entertainment. The 2-car garage provides ample space for parking and storage needs. Situated on almost an acre close to town, this property offers the best of both worlds – a tranquil retreat with easy access to restaurants, schools, & shopping!
